    "We compare our methods against several state-of-the-art approaches.",
    "The detailed results are presented in Table III, Table IV, and Table V.1) WebVision Results: As illustrated in Table III, we compare our proposed ANL-CE and ANL-FL methods against several state-of-the-art approaches, including GCE [12], SCE [13], APL [14], and AFL [42].",
    "For the ILSVRC12 validation set, ANL-FL achieves the best accuracy of 65.56%, followed closely by ANL-CE with 65.00%.",
